.com/pytorch/pytorch/pull/9277.diff", "patch_url": "https://github.com/pytorch/pytorch/pull/9277.patch"}, "body_html": "<p>THCStream was recently moved to ATen by <a class=\"user-mention\" data-hovercard-type=\"user\" data-hovercard-url=\"/hovercards?user_id=38511765\" data-octo-click=\"hovercard-link-click\" data-octo-dimensions=\"link_type:self\" href=\"https://github.com/mruberry\">@mruberry</a>: <a class=\"issue-link js-issue-link\" data-error-text=\"Failed to load issue title\" data-id=\"336758501\" data-permission-text=\"Issue title is private\" data-url=\"https://github.com/pytorch/pytorch/issues/8997\" data-hovercard-type=\"pull_request\" data-hovercard-url=\"/pytorch/pytorch/pull/8997/hovercard\" href=\"https://github.com/pytorch/pytorch/pull/8997\">#8997</a>. This PR now introduces a guard class that replaces <code>AutoStream</code> from <code>torch/csrc/</code> and also uses this new stream interface.</p>\n<p>I had to extend the <code>CUDAStream</code> interface with unchecked calls, so that we can reset the stream without throwing an exception in the guard's destructor.</p>\n<p><a class=\"user-mention\" data-hovercard-type=\"user\" data-hovercard-url=\"/hovercards?user_id=655866\" data-octo-click=\"hovercard-link-click\" data-octo-dimensions=\"link_type:self\" href=\"https://github.com/colesbury\">@colesbury</a> <a class=\"user-mention\" data-hovercard-type=\"user\" data-hovercard-url=\"/hovercards?user_id=4583066\" data-octo-click=\"hovercard-link-click\" data-octo-dimensions=\"link_type:self\" href=\"https://github.com/apaszke\">@apaszke</a> <a class=\"user-mention\" data-hovercard-type=\"user\" data-hovercard-url=\"/hovercards?user_id=13564\" data-octo-click=\"hovercard-link-click\" data-octo-dimensions=\"link_type:self\" href=\"https://github.com/ezyang\">@ezyang</a></p>\n<p><span class=\"issue-keyword tooltipped tooltipped-se\" aria-label=\"This pull request closes issue #7800.\">Fixes</span> <a class=\"issue-link js-issue-link\" data-error-text=\"Failed to load issue title\" data-id=\"325894266\" data-permission-text=\"Issue title is private\" data-url=\"https://github.com/pytorch/pytorch/issues/7800\" data-hovercard-type=\"issue\" data-hovercard-url=\"/pytorch/pytorch/issues/7800/hovercard\" href=\"https://github.com/pytorch/pytorch/issues/7800\">#7800</a></p>", "body_text": "THCStream was recently moved to ATen by @mruberry: #8997. This PR now introduces a guard class that replaces AutoStream from torch/csrc/ and also uses this new stream interface.\nI had to extend the CUDAStream interface with unchecked calls, so that we can reset the stream without throwing an exception in the guard's destructor.\n@colesbury @apaszke @ezyang\nFixes #7800", "body": "THCStream was recently moved to ATen by @mruberry: https://github.com/pytorch/pytorch/pull/8997. This PR now introduces a guard class that replaces `AutoStream` from `torch/csrc/` and also uses this new stream interface.\r\n\r\nI had to extend the `CUDAStream` interface with unchecked calls, so that we can reset the stream without throwing an exception in the guard's destructor.\r\n\r\n@colesbury @apaszke @ezyang \r\n\r\nFixes https://github.com/pytorch/pytorch/issues/7800"}